{"tid":729613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙美女記者直播報導時世界盃時遭男強吻","createTime":"2018-07-04T16:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T23:27:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d140d44f70a53c73086c7fdf39bc634295569c","tid":729613,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://as.com/tikitakas/imagenes/2018/07/03/portada/1530625160_827115_1530625426_noticia_normal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fas.com%2Ftikitakas%2Fimagenes%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2Fportada%2F1530625160_827115_1530625426_noticia_normal.jpg&h=09c2ce1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DG9QpDxXoAAhHf-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDG9QpDxXoAAhHf-.jpg&h=717a497c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙女記者Maria Gomez採訪俄羅斯世界盃時遭男子強吻，她在Twitter上載片段，並表示原本不想追究，但最終決定公開短片，希望向認為只是開玩笑的人表達，這並不是玩笑，無幽默感可言，亦是絕不正常。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ewqe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fewqe2.jpg&h=7cd9d015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她早前採訪一名西班球迷，詢問他對西班牙足總會長的看法時，被該名球途稱呼靚女，又問其叫甚麼名字。世界盃期間已發生多宗女記者採訪時遭男球迷性騷擾，瑞典電視節目主持Mahlin Wahlberg亦被強吻，哥倫比亞記者Julieth Gonzalez Theran較早前直播時更被途人「胸襲」。"},{"pid":"37fda468eee1f92cd801b99a52e07883a9f47c73","tid":729613,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f03f4ed38673bc79a60e2694ea38ee7e307fb68","tid":729613,"uid":62350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc96218f4cbda6bf8570d9848fe9ac12a1453d0","tid":729613,"uid":57226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"波台手足<img src=